episodes.title: Inside the Nation of Islam: Cult or Community? With Bro. Daniel Omowale
episodes.description:
Peace family, join me as I speak with former NOI member Daniel Omowale as he discusses his experiences in the NOI, the evolution of the organization ranging from the leadership of Elijah Muhammad to that of Louis Farrakhan, and its practice of using Black nationalist rhetoric, religious dogma, and political and racial controversy to exploit poor and working-class African Americans.

Tap in here: https://streamyard.com/6fartg3c9p
